title: Philippines GDP Deflator
description: GDP Deflator in Philippines increased to 110.04 points in the third quarter of 2022 from 108.10 points in the second quarter of 2022. GDP Deflator in Philippines averaged 67.04 points from 1981 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 110.04 points in the third quarter of 2022 and a record low of 12.87 points in the first quarter of 1981. This page provides - Philippines GDP Deflator - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Philippine Statistics Authority
